OL,3,CWhy are so many festivals cancelling
OL,4,Cthis summer?
OL,6,FTo date, 43 UK music have been called
OL,7,Foff this summer. Factoring in last
OL,8,Fyear, the total number which have
OL,9,Fcancelled is more than 80 over an 18
OL,10,Fmonth period.
OL,12,FThe Association of Independent
OL,13,FFestivals (AIF), an industry body
OL,14,Frepresenting more than 200 , says they
OL,15,Ffear that figure could exceed 100 by
OL,16,Fthe end of the year.
OL,18,FLive music is more popular than ever,
OL,19,Fwith more than 37 million ticket sales
OL,20,Facross concerts last year according to
OL,21,Fthe UK Music Report for 2023.
