OL,3,CWhy are so many festivals cancelling
OL,4,Cthis summer?
OL,6,FSimon Clarke, the festival director
OL,7,Fsaid: "It has become increasingly
OL,8,Fdifficult for independent festivals to
OL,9,Foperate in in the current climate. We
OL,10,Fknow we're not alone and many other
OL,11,Ffestivals are in a similar situation.
OL,13,F"It's a tough financial market out
OL,14,Fthere, it's tough so sell tickets
OL,15,Fbecause people haven't got the money
OL,16,Fand it's also tough to put events on
OL,17,Fbecause the cost of doing so is
OL,18,Fgetting so high".
