OL,3,CWhy are so many festivals cancelling
OL,4,Cthis summer?
OL,6,FCovid obviously dealt the festival
OL,7,Findustry a huge blow. One in six never
OL,8,Freturned after the pandemic. Those
OL,9,Fwhich did survive have struggled to
OL,10,Fbreak even ever since. Overall
OL,11,Foperational costs have risen by more
OL,12,Fthan a third in the last couple of
OL,13,Fyears. Inflation has made the cost of
OL,14,Fputting on events much more expensive.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/9
