OL,3,CWhy are so many festivals cancelling
OL,4,Cthis summer?
OL,6,FMany smaller festivals also lack the
OL,7,Fcash reserves to pay the production
OL,8,Fcosts up front. It is an industry
OL,9,Fwhich is hugely reliant on temporary
OL,10,Flabour and the leasing of equipment.
OL,11,FBrexit has restricted access for many
OL,12,Ffestival workers from Europe and made
OL,13,Fthe logistics pool smaller.
OL,15,FMany service providers also want
OL,16,Fpayment up front. However, if festival
OL,17,Fattendees leave it late to buy
OL,18,Ftickets, some organisers decide to
OL,19,Fcancel altogether rather than run at a
OL,20,Floss.
