OL,3,CWhy are so many festivals cancelling
OL,4,Cthis summer?
OL,6,FJohn Rostron, chief executive of AIF,
OL,7,Ftold ITV News: "As you come towards
OL,8,Fthe event, you hire lots of companies,
OL,9,Fsupply chain companies, and hundreds,
OL,10,Fif not thousands of freelancers.
OL,12,F"Then of course you might have
OL,13,Fvolunteering opportunities too. So the
OL,14,Feffect every time a festival goes
OL,15,Fdown, the repercussions are huge.
OL,17,F"Loads of jobs lost, loads of
OL,18,Fvolunteering opportunities are lost
OL,19,Fand future festival headliners do not
OL,20,Fget their first steps onto a stage."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/9
