OL,3,CWhy are so many festivals cancelling
OL,4,Cthis summer?
OL,6,FThe AIF is running a campaign to call
OL,7,Fon whoever wins the next election to
OL,8,Fcommit to a reduction in VAT on
OL,9,Ffestival ticket sales from 20% to 5%
OL,10,Ffor the next three years in their
OL,11,Fcampaign. Giving festival organisers a
OL,12,Fchance to reinvest.
OL,14,FLove Saves The Day is a dance and
OL,15,Felectronic music festival which runs
OL,16,Fover two days with more than 60,000
OL,17,Fattendees. Tom Paine, the CEO, says
OL,18,Fthe industry would use any support
OL,19,Fpackage to move from surviving to
OL,20,Fthriving.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/9
